check_and_trim_all_image_pairs_from_site_dir

- loop over all possible image pair combinations in an input SITE_DIR
- check and trim all image pairs for a min/max temporal baseline




process_all_image_pairs_dir folders_in_list

- make a list of all img_pair_dir folders for an input SITE_DIR
- loop over the list and compute DoB, STD, NORMPROD for each image pair
- distribute these jobs individually for parallel processing
